, {\"ngram\": \"the city's heart\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At least, that is plan A, anyway - Emmanuel Macron, the French president, confirmed an off-river contingency for the first time on Monday.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French president\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plan\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"-river\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement Excitement has not quite taken hold in Paris yet.\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.292611795293785e-53, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Advertisement Excitement\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Decorations around the city remain discrete for a Games awarded to the French capital in September 2017.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.4336697413389455e-11, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Decorations\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"a Games\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The City Hall has been plastered withOlympicregalia, but the focus of messaging has primarily been on practicality - \\\"anticiper les jeux\\\" (anticipate the Games), as posters on the Paris Metro, the city's subway system, depict it.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Town_hall\", \"score\": 0.9993879078636672, \"rank\": 0.0006124670138024412, \"text\": \"City Hall\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Town_hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Town_hall\"}, {\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\", \"score\": 0.9999998407884176, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Metro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"withOlympicregalia\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"practicality\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"anticiper les jeux\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"posters\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's subway system\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The past few years have seen plenty of focus on staging the Games, but there has been much more discussion about the practical impact.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The past few years\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"focus\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"much more discussion\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"the practical impact\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities have battled and quarrelled to meet deadlines and targets.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Authorities\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"deadlines\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"targets\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been fears around security, heightened byRussia's invasion ofUkraineand the Israel-Gaza conflict, with the audacious, river-basedopening ceremony- set to be the first time a Games has not opened in a stadium - a particular area of concern.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fears\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"byRussia's invasion\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"ofUkraineand\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"the Israel-Gaza conflict\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"the audacious, river-basedopening ceremony- set\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"a Games\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"a particular area\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"concern\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add in worries about transport disruption and the threats of strike action from unions with public sector workers, including police, demanding pay concessions for the extra work anticipated for the Games, and the build-up has been anything but smooth.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"worries\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"transport disruption\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the threats\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"strike action\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"unions\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"public sector workers\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"pay concessions\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"the extra work\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even 'les bouquinistes', the booksellers who maintain a 400-year tradition on the banks of the River Seine, erupted in protest at the prospect of temporary removal for theopening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even 'les bouquinistes\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the booksellers\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"a 400-year tradition\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1689}, {\"ngram\": \"protest\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"the prospect\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary removal\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"ceremony\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But now, the focus should turn to what else the Games has to offer before theOlympicsbegin on July 26 (although the men's andwomen's competitions for soccerand rugby sevens begin on July 24), with the Paralympic Games to follow from August 28 until September 8.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsbegin\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's andwomen's competitions\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"soccerand rugby\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the French edition,\\\" joked Emmanuel Gregoire, the mayor of Paris' first deputy, when asked about optimism before the Games at a press briefing this month.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.4336697413389455e-11, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2091, \"end\": 2099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"score\": 0.9999999999708962, \"rank\": 2.947774979832408e-11, \"text\": \"Emmanuel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\"}, {\"begin\": 2100, \"end\": 2108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Gregoire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.248151585560054e-52, \"text\": \"Gregoire\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_