to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"the Middle East\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"inflationary pressures\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2959}, {\"ngram\": \"screaming headlines aboutbedbug infestations\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is safe to say the world could do with a little bit of joy and maybe the Games can provide that.\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3087}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The question now is whether Paris is ready.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3155, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.292611795293785e-53, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The question\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The permanent sites are ready.\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The permanent sites\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is aiming to host a sustainable, green-focused Games, with 95 per cent of tournament venues either temporary or using already existing infrastructure.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3203, \"end\": 3208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.292611795293785e-53, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sustainable, green-focused Games\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3261}, {\"ngram\": \"95 per cent\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\"