verages\", \"from\": 13638, \"to\": 13650}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio 2016\", \"from\": 13670, \"to\": 13678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They want to use 100 per cent renewable energy and intend to achieve this using modifications such as connecting all venues to the grid, therefore limiting the use of temporary diesel generators.\", \"from\": 13680, \"to\": 13875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100 per cent renewable energy\", \"from\": 13697, \"to\": 13726}, {\"ngram\": \"modifications\", \"from\": 13760, \"to\": 13773}, {\"ngram\": \"all venues\", \"from\": 13793, \"to\": 13803}, {\"ngram\": \"the grid\", \"from\": 13807, \"to\": 13815}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 13836, \"to\": 13843}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary diesel generators\", \"from\": 13847, \"to\": 13874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They want all sites accessible by public transport and are even \\\"doubling the plant-based food to reach a target of 1kg of CO2 per meal, compared with the 2.3kg French average\\\", according to Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 13876, \"to\": 14078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14067, \"end\": 14077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4023274753383633e-57, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all sites\", \"from\": 13886, \"to\": 13895}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport\", \"from\": 13910, \"to\": 13926}, {\"ngram\": \"the plant-based food\", \"from\": 13950, \"to\": 13970}, {\"ngram\": \"a target\", \"from\": 13980, \"to\": 13988}, {\"ngram\": \"1kg\", \"from\": 13992, \"to\": 13995}, {\"ngram\": \"CO2\", \"from\": 13999, \"to\": 14002}, {\"ngram\": \"meal\", \"from\": 14007, \"to\": 14011}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2.3kg French average\", \"from\": 14027, \"to\": 14051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ensuring a lasting impact in disadvantaged communities is also on the agenda.\", \"from\": 14080, \"to\": 14157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lasting impact\", \"from\": 14089, \"to\": 14105}, {\"ngram\": \"disadvantaged communities\", \"from\": 14109, \"to\": 14134}, {\"ngram\": \"the agenda\", \"from\": 14146, \"to\": 14156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saint-Denis, in particular, is set to benefit, with the athletes' accommodation planned to be turned into 2,800 homes after the Games, 25 per cent of which will be social housing.\", \"from\": 14158, \"to\": 14337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14158, \"end\": 14169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.074555694170214e-14, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes' accommodation\", \"from\": 14210, \"to\": 14237}, {\"ngram\": \"2,800 homes\", \"from\": 14264, \"to\": 14275}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 14282, \"to\": 14291}, {\"ngram\": \"25 per cent\", \"from\": 14293, \"to\": 14304}, {\"ngram\": \"social housing\", \"from\": 14322, \"to\": 14336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The area also stands to gain renovated pools, including the Aquatics Center, which will replace a 50-year-old 25-metre pool.\", \"from\": 14338, \"to\": 14462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The area\", \"from\": 14338, \"to\": 14346}, {\"ngram\": \"renovated pools\", \"from\": 14367, \"to\": 14382}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatics Center\", \"from\": 14394, \"to\": 14413}, {\"ngram\": \"a 50-year-old 25-metre pool\", \"from\": 14434, \"to\": 14461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement This, along with cycling, will assist a sporting legacy.\", \"from\": 14464, \"to\": 14535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 14495, \"to\": 14502}, {\"ngram\": \"a sporting legacy\", \"from\": 14516, \"to\": 14533}]}, {\"sentence\":